In [18]:
medals_by_year = df.groupby('Year')['Medal'].count()
plt.figure(figsize=(12,6))
sns.lineplot(x=medals_by_year.index,y=medals_by_year.values,marker='o')
plt.title('Total Medals Awarded Per Year (1976-2008)')
plt.xlabel('Year')
plt.ylabel('Number of Medals')
plt.grid(True)

The trend of total medals awarded per year shows an increasing pattern over time, with a notable jump in the number of medals awarded from 1976 to 2008.

In [20]:
sport_medals = df.groupby('Sport')['Medal'].count().sort_values(ascending=False).head(10)
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 6))
sns.barplot(x=sport_medals.index, y=sport_medals.values, palette='magma')
plt.title('Top 10 Sports by Total Medals')
plt.xlabel('Sport')
plt.ylabel('Number of Medals')
plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
plt.show()

Aquatics is the sport with the highest number of medals, followed by Athletics and Rowing, reflecting their prominence in the Summer Olympics.

In [21]:
top_5_countries = df.groupby('Country')['Medal'].count().nlargest(5).index
df_top_countries = df[df['Country'].isin(top_5_countries)]
medals_by_year_country = df_top_countries.groupby(['Year', 'Country'])['Medal'].count().reset_index()
plt.figure(figsize=(14, 7))
sns.lineplot(data=medals_by_year_country, x='Year', y='Medal', hue='Country', marker='o')
plt.title('Medal Distribution Over Years for Top 5 Countries (1976-2008)')
plt.xlabel('Year')
plt.ylabel('Number of Medals')
plt.grid(True)
plt.legend(title='Country')
Out[21]:
<matplotlib.legend.Legend at 0x1e179cc50d0>

This line plot visualizes how the top 5 medal-winning countries (United States, Soviet Union, Australia, Germany, and China) have performed in terms of medal counts over the different Olympic years. It allows for a comparative analysis of their historical performance trends.

United States & Australia has constant domainance performance in medal winning every year since 1975 to 2008.

Soviet Union (Russia) has continuously decline in medal over time except 1982 where it boycotted entire olympics.

Germany as a whole country inlcuding (west and east), saw continous decline over period of time.

country_medal_type = country_medal_type.sort_values(by='Total', ascending=False).head(10)
